1098
01:08:04,254 --> 01:08:06,169
Did you get injured?

1099
01:08:06,256 --> 01:08:07,344
I did.

1100
01:08:07,431 --> 01:08:08,431
What happened?

1101
01:08:10,738 --> 01:08:15,352
I got caught a
