1110
01:08:43,075 --> 01:08:44,075
Are you better now?

1111
01:08:48,167 --> 01:08:51,649
Son, right this
second I sure am.

1112
01:09:24,856 --> 01:09:26,597
William!

1113
01:09:26,684 --> 01:09:27,946
