1114
01:09:42,047 --> 01:09:43,047
Kimmie?

1115
01:10:12,991 --> 01:10:14,253
What's wrong?

1116
01:10:14,340 --> 01:10:16,995
Don't be alarmed.

1117
01:10:17,082 --> 01:10:18,649
What?

1118
01:10:18,736 --> 01:10:21,086
