kind words and run with them.

1262
01:19:21,713 --> 01:19:24,020
Your work.

1263
01:19:24,107 --> 01:19:27,632
I love your work.

1264
01:19:27,719 --> 01:19:28,719
Action!

1265
01:19:43,648 --> 01:19:46,912
