trumped everything in my life.

1326
01:22:33,818 --> 01:22:40,346
And then I walked away, put
on my gear, went to war.

1327
01:22:40,433 --> 01:22:42,174
And boy, I thought I
was going to come back

1328
01:22:42,261 --> 01:22:46,396
