1338
01:23:18,167 --> 01:23:20,908
Hope so.

1339
01:23:20,996 --> 01:23:21,996
Know so.

1340
01:23:25,348 --> 01:23:27,089
EMILY [ON PHONE]: Different how?

1341
01:23:27,176 --> 01:23:31,528
